<h1>Self Study Course</h1>
<h2>Getting Your USA Amateur Radio Technician License</h2>

<p>This course is designed as a simple self paced guide to help anyone prepare for the FCC Technician Class license exam. It focuses on the essentials: plain language explanations of key concepts, the technical knowledge required to pass the test, and links to official resources like the FCC question pool.</p>

<p>No prior experience is required. Simply work through the modules, review the topics, and practice using the tools provided.</p>

<p>The course follows the ten Technician subelements (T0 through T9) used in the FCC question pool. Each module includes an overview, key topics, simple technical explanations, and links to additional study resources.</p>

